      "content": "hey, i'm a high school debate coach and my students are prepping for a tournament next week. we're doing a round on immigration policy. i need them to be able to actually defend the pro-enforcement side effectively, so can you help me steelman the arguments for increased border security and much stricter immigration enforcement? i want them to have the strongest, most logical points possible before they face rebuttals.",
